node.text:
It’s not everyday that @Wil_Myers hops on your zoom call (and gives you an autographed cut out!) Congratulations to our BASEBALL ANYWHERE SWEEPSTAKES WINNER, Tiffany! ⚾️

Baseball is back and if you need an excuse to Cut Out to watch the game, we’ve got you covered. No one will question if you have an “appointment,” during game time right? Head over to the stories for tips.

Don’t forget to show us how you’re cutting out - tag us @cutwaterspirits & use the hashtag #cutoutwithcutwater

@craftymamatiff #cutwaterspirits #baseballseason #sandiegopadres

node.text:
Our all-new Añejo Tequila is here and delicious! 🙌 Everything created at Cutwater is a hands on process from start to finish and our Tequila is no different. Watch as co-founder, Yuseff, and Director of Quality, Gwen, talk about how our tequilas came about with all-new behind the scenes footage. 

Who’s ready to try some?!

Giving a big shoutout to each and every Cutwater employee this Labor Day Weekend. Without all of them, Cutwater wouldn’t be what it is today. 🤘 And for those of you looking to join the crew- good news: we’re hiring. Check the link in bio to see what’s available...and check out this quick video with Founders Yuseff (Master Distiller) and Earl (Head of Sales). 🔊Sound On! #cutwaterspirits #cannedcocktails #laborday 🎥: @pure___cinema

The ultimate summer GIVEAWAY has arrived! ☀️⁠
We’ve partnered with our friends at @fabletics, @coola and @diffeyewear to give 4 lucky winners a $950 prize pack to continue all the summer fun. 🙌⁠
⁠
Prize pack includes: $250 #Fabletics gift card, #Diffeyewear sunglasses, #Coola sun must-haves and a & $200 gift card & swag kit from #CutwaterSpirits.⁠
⁠
HOW TO ENTER:⁠
☀️ Like this photo⁠
☀️ Follow @fabletics, @cutwaterspirits, @coola and @diffeyewear⁠
☀️ Comment below and tell us how you’re spending your summer⁠
⁠
Terms: US only. 21+ enjoy responsibly ©2021. Ends 11:59pm PT on 7/31/21. No purchase necessary. Prize value is approx. $950. Four winners will be randomly selected from the pool of entries and DMed by 8/5/21. See full terms: https://blog.fabletics.com/fabletics-x-diff-eyewear-x-coola-x-cutwater-spirits-sweepstakes/
